title: Navigating the Common Challenges of Marriage, Part 8
itunes:author: John Fuller & Greg Smalley
itunes:summary: No matter how much you love your spouse, he or she can still drive you crazy. John talks with Greg and Erin about how they work through their annoying habits with each other.
